item.title: [PI] Editing tabs
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

reventix:

The headings are in RSinterfaces, for instance Owners,Admins and Moderators but the actual names like “ace” and “honor” are not in there, i have looked everywhere for them…

The actual names are sent from the server to the client.
Search in the server for em and you should find them.
Each person handles it differently so I can’t say exactly where it will be found in the server
